67.0	Randy_Couture	Randy Couture	Randy Duane Couture . Couture has competed in a record 15 title fights. He holds the most title reigns in the UFC with five. His last fight with Lyoto Machida marked his 24th fight in the UFC, the third most amount of fights in the UFC (Tito Ortiz is first with 26 and Matt Hughes is second with 25). Couture is one of the first members of the UFC Hall of Fame. He is the only person over the age of 40 to have won a UFC championship fight, having done so four times.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2a/Randy_Couture_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg/220px-Randy_Couture_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg
